328
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,720
 Ali zato smo mi roditelji tu,

329
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,560
 da im pomognemo oko tih finesa,

330
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:34,540
 da ih podržimo tamo kad vidimo

331
00:32:34,540 --> 00:32:37,920
