00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:14,040
 I obično ta djeca im je skroz drugačije sklonosti nekad.

375
00:34:14,040 --> 00:34:14,320
 Je.

376
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:16,780
 A ima i onih koji nastave

377
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:18,400
