00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:26,360
 Možemo

409
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:28,580
 stremiti ka istom cilju,

410
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:29,100
 što je ok,

411
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:31,180
 ali ti ćeš imati svoj put.

412
00:35:31,180 --> 00:35:32,260
 A ja ću imati svoj put.

413
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:33,520
 jer su

414
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:35,520
 moje uvjerenja,

